  "comment": "Orion W40 with 7 40W 4in1 RGBL LEDs with Zoom: The Orion W40 projector is a compact, lightweight, fast and extremely bright wash moving head that projects a concentrated beam and a striking wash effect, a custom designed optical system with 7 40W RGBL LEDs creates an excellent mix of colors and a Zoom range of 4º to 45º that allows you to cover large areas.\nThe unit’s small size also allows for ultra-fast and smooth pan and tilt movement",
